<taxonomicName box="[563,640,1815,1839]" class="Insecta" family="Hybotidae" genus="Drapetis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="17" pageNumber="18" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zamba">zamba</taxonomicName>
” means “forest” in Lingala.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
